info.name: 10b) Spine Error or Warning Codes
info.description:
https://nhsd-confluence.digital.nhs.uk/display/APIMC/Error+Handling

Spine ErrorOrWarning Codes:


https://simplifier.net/NHSDigitalSpine/Spine-ErrorOrWarningCode

CodeSystem: https://fhir.nhs.uk/R4/CodeSystem/Spine-ErrorOrWarningCode



Old EPS Code	New EPS Code	Display	FHIR Issue Type	Response Code	Definition
0007

INVALID_RESOURCE_ID

The resource ID was not valid. For example a NHS Number is presented which is not a valid NHS Number.	code-invalid	400	The resource ID was not valid. For example a NHS Number is presented which is not a valid NHS Number.
0008

MISSING_VALUE

Missing value	value	400	There was a missing value in the request. For example - a name update that is missing the surname. The missing value will be presented in the display.
0099

RESOURCE_VERSION_MISMATCH

Resource version mismatch	conflict	409	The resource version has changed since your last read, so the update has been rejected.

exec: console.log("Spine ErrorOrWarningCodes Displays - The resource ID was not valid. For example a NHS Number is presented which is not a valid NHS Number.");
console.log("Spine ErrorOrWarningCodes Displays - Resource version mismatch");
